      "bookSlug": "matthew",
      "chapterNumber": 3,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Matthew 3:2",
      "text": "ܘܐܡܪ ܬܘܒܘ ܩܪܒܬ ܠܗ ܡܠܟܘܬܐ ܕܫܡܝܐ ܀",
